    ```tactics
    have h7 : ПҲ вҲҲ construction T hT i := by
      apply T.imp_closed
      exact h1
      exact hi
    ```
    This creates `h7 : ПҲ вҲҲ construction T hT i`.

5.  We now have `h5 i : В¬(ПҲ вҲҲ construction T hT i)` and `h7 : ПҲ вҲҲ construction T hT i`. This is a contradiction.
